			<section class="px-8 sm:px-12 lg:px-16 py-32 border-t border-slate-700/50">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-20 items-center">
						<div>
							<h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Our Story</h2>
							<div class="space-y-6 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed text-lg">
								<p class="hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors duration-300">
									Logan's 3D Creations began with a simple fascination: the ability to transform digital ideas into tangible reality. What started as a hobby quickly evolved into a passion for pushing the boundaries of what's possible with 3D printing technology.
								</p>
								<p class="hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors duration-300">
									Today, we specialize in creating high-quality, detailed 3D printed products ranging from educational dinosaur models and mythical dragons to functional fidget toys and custom prototypes. Every piece is crafted with attention to detail and a commitment to excellence.
								</p>
								<p class="hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors duration-300">
									Beyond creating products, we're dedicated to education and community engagement. Through workshops, demonstrations, and hands-on learning experiences, we share the excitement and potential of 3D printing with the next generation of makers and innovators.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800/50 to-slate-900/50 rounded-3xl p-10 border border-slate-700/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all duration-500 group">
