								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center group/item hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors duration-300">
									<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-emerald-400 rounded-full mr-4 group-hover/item:scale-110 transition-transform duration-200"></div>
									Premium filaments and materials
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center group/item hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors duration-300">
									<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-emerald-400 rounded-full mr-4 group-hover/item:scale-110 transition-transform duration-200"></div>
									Professional post-processing tools
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center group/item hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors duration-300">
									<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-emerald-400 rounded-full mr-4 group-hover/item:scale-110 transition-transform duration-200"></div>
									Quality control and testing equipment
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Precision & Innovation</h2>
							<div class="space-y-6 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed text-lg">
								<p class="hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors duration-300">
									Our workshop is equipped with the latest 3D printing technology, from high-resolution resin printers for intricate details to large-format FDM printers for bigger projects.
								</p>
								<p class="hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors duration-300">
									We work with a wide range of materials including PLA, PETG, ABS, TPU, and specialty filaments to ensure each project uses the best material for its intended purpose.
								</p>
								<p class="hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors duration-300">
									Every print goes through rigorous quality control to ensure it meets our high standards before reaching our customers.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<!-- Contact CTA -->
			<section class="px-8 sm:px-12 lg:px-16 py-32">
